02851                                         #endif
02852                                 }
02853                         }
02854                         else
02855                         {
02856                                 #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02857                                 *output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02858                                 #else
02859                                 *output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02860                                 #endif
02861                                 while (--i)
02862                                 {                                                               /*U_TO_U*/
02863                                         input0 += inputOffset;
02864                                         input1 += inputOffset;
02865                                         input2 += inputOffset;
02866                                         input3 += inputOffset;
02867                                         input4 += inputOffset;
02868 
02869                                         output0 += outputOffset;
02870                                         output1 += outputOffset;
02871                                         output2 += outputOffset;
02872                                         output3 += outputOffset;
02873                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02874                                         output4 += outputOffset;
02875                                         #endif
02876                                         if ((*input0 ^ input0[-inputOffset]) || (*input1 ^ input1[-inputOffset]) || (*input2 ^ input2[-inputOffset]) || (*input3 ^ input3[-inputOffset]))
02877                                         {
02878                                                 break;
02879                                         }
02880                                         *output0 = output0[-outputOffset];
02881                                         *output1 = output1[-outputOffset];
02882                                         *output2 = output2[-outputOffset];
02883                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02884                                         *output3 = output3[-outputOffset];
02885                                         *output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02886                                         #else
02887                                         *output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02888                                         #endif
02889                                 }
02890                         }
02891                 }
02892                 if (--LineCount)
02893                 {
02894                         j++;
02895                         input0 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[0] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02896                         input1 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[1] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02897                         input2 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[2] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02898                         input3 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[3] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02899                         input4 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[4] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02900 
02901                         output0 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[0] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02902                         output1 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[1] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02903                         output2 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[2] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02904                         output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[3] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02905                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02906                         output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[4] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02907                         #endif
02908                 }
02909         }
02910         LH_END_PROC(LH_CALC_PROC_NAME)
02911         return 0;
02912 }
02913 #else
02914 {
02915 
02916         LH_UINT32 ein_regb;
02917         LH_UINT32 ein_regg;
02918         LH_UINT32 ein_regr;
02919         LH_LUT_DATA_TYPE * paNewVal0;

02921         LH_UINT32 ako1;
02922         LH_UINT32 ako2;

02926         long inputOffset,outputOffset;

02928         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE * input1 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)calcParam->inputData[1];
02929         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE * input2 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)calcParam->inputData[2];
02930         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE * input3 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)calcParam->inputData[3];

02933         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output1 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[1];
02934         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output2 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[2];
02935         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[3];
02936         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[4];
02937 
02938         LH_UINT16 * My_InputLut = (LH_UINT16 *)lutParam->inputLut;
02939         LH_LUT_DATA_TYPE * My_OutputLut = (LH_LUT_DATA_TYPE *)lutParam->outputLut;
02940         LH_LUT_DATA_TYPE * My_ColorLut = (LH_LUT_DATA_TYPE *)lutParam->colorLut;
02941 
02942         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE Mask = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)-1;
02943 
02944 #ifdef DEBUG_OUTPUT
02945         CMError err = noErr;
02946 #endif
02947         LH_START_PROC(LH_CALC_PROC_NAME)
02948 
02949         #if LH_DATA_IN_SIZE_16
02950         inputOffset = (long)calcParam->cmInputPixelOffset / 2;
02951         #else
02952         inputOffset = (long)calcParam->cmInputPixelOffset;
02953         #endif
02954         #if LH_DATA_OUT_SIZE_16
02955         outputOffset = (long)calcParam->cmOutputPixelOffset / 2;
02956         #else

02958         #endif
02959

02961                 Mask = 0;

02963 
02964 
02965         if ((calcParam->cmInputPixelOffset * calcParam->cmPixelPerLine == calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine) && (calcParam->cmOutputPixelOffset * calcParam->cmPixelPerLine == calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine))
02966         {
02967                 PixelCount = calcParam->cmPixelPerLine * calcParam->cmLineCount;
02968                 LineCount = 1;
02969         }
02970         else
02971         {
02972                 PixelCount = calcParam->cmPixelPerLine;
02973                 LineCount = calcParam->cmLineCount;
02974         }
02975         if (calcParam->copyAlpha )
02976         {
02977                         Mode = LH_CALC_ENGINE_U_TO_U;
02978         }
02979         else
02980         {
02981                 if (calcParam->clearMask)
02982                         Mode = LH_CALC_ENGINE_P_TO_U;
02983                 else
02984                         Mode = LH_CALC_ENGINE_P_TO_P;
02985         }
02986         j = 0;

02989                 i = PixelCount;
02990                 while (i)

02994                         register LH_UINT32 ko;
02995                         #endif

02997                         register LH_DATA_IN_TYPE aValIn;
02998                 #endif

03000                         register LH_UINT32 aVal;
03001                 #endif
03002                         #if LH_DATA_IN_SIZE_16
03003                                 aValIn = *input0 - ( *input0 >> ( LH_ADR_BREIT_EIN_LUT ));

03006                         ein_regr = ( My_InputLut[aValIn] * ( (1<<( 16-LH_ADR_BREIT_EIN_LUT )) - ko ) + My_InputLut[aValIn +1] * ko ) >>( 16-LH_ADR_BREIT_EIN_LUT );
03007
